ZH: 太阳能是一种用太阳能源转换成电能的技术。
EN: Solar energy is a technology that converts solar energy into electrical energy.

ZH: 我们家安装了太阳能热水器。
EN: We have installed a solar water heater in our home.

ZH: 太阳能发电系统可以减少对化石燃料的依赖。
EN: Solar power systems can reduce dependence on fossil fuels.

